sentences: Kyle has been active in more than 11 bands in her career, including Black Audience, Jayanthi Kyle and the Crybabies, Romantica, Gospel Machine, Davis Bain Band, Passed Presents, Give Get Sistet, Miss Pennie's Microphone, and The Blacker The Berry Arts Collective.
Kyle was born c. 1979 to an Indian father and a Native American and black mother.
The song,  inspired by the deaths of Eric Garner and Michael Brown, was first performed at the Million March MN rally on December 13, 2014.
